data.description: Serenity in suburbia perfectly describes the setting for this wonderful Ferris charmer that has been well cared for by the current owner. Nestled in Ferris and convenient to area retail and I-75 and convenient to schools. Open living and dining areas flow into each other for a functional living space that is perfect for family game nights or a prime entertainment space. The hardwood floors are exceptional and the updates and upgrades on this home are must see. Custom bead-board work, upgraded paint, a large backyard, large bedrooms, kitchen and bath remodels, upgraded fixtures and exceptional flooring make this home the best buy in town. Sure to sell quickly so call today and schedule your showing.
